videos.headline: McKinney drops a dime for 90-yard Eastern Kentucky TD
videos.description: Parker McKinney lobs one over the top to Keyion Dixon who breaks away for a 90-yard touchdown for Eastern Kentucky.

videos.headline: Legassey nails game-winning 47-yard FG for Troy
videos.description: Evan Leggassey makes a 47-yard field goal to lift Troy to a 31-29 win over Eastern Kentucky.
